{
  "texts": [
    "However, the strongest effects could not be observed for the treatment variable.",
    "Instead, they were visible for the variable encoding whether a student passed the APA requirements.",
    "Passing the APA requirements strongly affected the perception of Comprehensiveness, Motivation, Regulation, Progress and Helpfulness.",
    "These effects were all positive, meaning that passing the APA requirement has an overall stronger influence on the dependent variables than the treatment variable, i.e., participants were likely more influenced by whether they passed the APA requirements than by the treatment variable.",
    "Concerning RQ 1 (To what degree can we automate the analytic scoring procedures needed to provide highly informative feedback to learners concerning the content of their essays?"
  ]
}